      • loadVenue

        public void loadVenue(java.lang.String venueId,
                      VenueDatabase.OnLoadVenueListeners listeners)
        Load a Venue using its venueId (returned from listVenues) Load type: Classic Load With this load type, there are three listeners: 1] onLoadProgress: gets called whenever loading progresses, this is a good time to update any loading progress indicators. 2] onLoadVenue: gets called when loading is complete, this is a good time to end any loading progress indicators. 3] onLoadFailed: gets called when there's been a problem loading.
        Parameters:
        venueId - - the id of the venue to load
        listeners - - the lifecycle listeners to be called while loading the venue

      • downloadLatestVenue

        public void downloadLatestVenue(java.lang.String venueId,
                                VenueDatabase.OnLoadVenueListeners listeners)
        Downloads the specified Venue using its venueId. The download will happen even if the latest venue already exists on the device.
        Parameters:
        venueId - - the id of the venue to load
        listeners - - the lifecycle listeners to be called while loading the venue

      • loadVenueAndMap

        public void loadVenueAndMap(java.lang.String venueId,
                            java.lang.String search,
                            VenueDatabase.OnLoadVenueAndMapListeners listeners)
        Load an Venue using its venueId (returned from listVenues) Load type: Fast Load With this load type, there are four listeners: 1] onLoadedInitialView: gets called almost immediately with a view. The receiver is expected to add this view to a the view hierarchy by calling setContentView(). 2] onLoadProgress: gets called whenever loading progresses, this is a good time to update any loading progress indicators. 3] onLoadCompleted: gets called when loading is complete, this is a good time to end any loading progress indicators. 4] onLoadFailed: gets called when there's been a problem loading.
        Parameters:
        venueId - - the id of the venue to load
        search - an optional search term (pass null if none)
        listeners - - the lifecycle listeners to be called while loading the venue
